Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.85,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.85,0:00:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.99,0:00:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.86,0:00:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.84,0:00:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.69,0:00:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.99,0:01:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.95,0:01:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一則新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.92,0:01:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠著開發電腦軟體急速成長的\N日和產業倒閉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.79,0:01:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連帶受到衝擊的相關企業有\N理參電器、輕井商事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.73,0:01:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及擔商會\N都被迫捲入連鎖破產的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.74,0:01:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以上是今天的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.92,0:02:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師運氣真背啊\N明明好不容易找到工作了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,妳不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個,妳看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.87,0:02:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間“擔商會”就是\N妳爸爸介紹給他的公司吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.17,0:02:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師現在可能打擊太大\N而臥床不起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.78,0:02:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還上吊了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師好可憐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,要遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,要遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#75 專一的愛情!八神和明日菜\N是學不會教訓的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐一臉悶悶不樂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是為了五代的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此,錄用他的公司…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.38,0:03:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的運氣真的很背啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,有何貴幹啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明天去探望一下\N明日菜小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.47,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?明日菜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.54,0:04:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次跟教練相親的那位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.32,0:04:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚\N聽說她一直臥病不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去探望她一下\N順便去加深跟她的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,你煩不煩啊\N我已經有喜歡的女人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才死腦筋耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.36,0:04:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人在哪裡?\N至少介紹一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼企圖?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那種女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫“那種女人”啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.52,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種好像酒桶穿著運動服的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在看誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然說“酒桶穿著運動服”\N他還真會形容啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.47,0:05:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此,的確是個美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不明白你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,去探望明日菜小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟他們說好了\N說你明天會去探望她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又自作主張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了,我也會跟你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,等一等,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,真拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.23,0:05:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒跟相親對象做個了斷嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒斷清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,音無小姐請妳放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.55,0:05:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著這次的探望\N我一定會跟她斷得一乾二淨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不太好吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.39,0:05:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不希望三鷹去做個了斷嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.23,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳跟五代的感情\N有所進展嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.13,0:06:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相親對象的條件比我好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對三鷹也比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳倒是蠻乾脆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟五代之間到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼問\N我們什麼都沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要出去啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,說不定會晚點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟阪本去喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要太消沈喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.01,0:06:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,反正公司到處都有嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.71,0:06:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭,這麼一點小事\N我根本不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然強顏歡笑\N但背影卻看得出來在哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟那像從天堂被推入地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪他會難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?怎麼一副兇巴巴的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.28,0:07:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把五代老師\N介紹去快要倒閉的公司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.12,0:07:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那件事啊\N我沒有想到那家公司會倒閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就負起責任啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責?怎麼負責?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫他介紹別的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別的公司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.84,0:07:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉\N要不然五代老師太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我也沒有臉見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再有本事\N也無法再幫他的忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老婆,放洗澡水,我要洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,是叔叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.04,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬,我得先去個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己先去九条家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔不在,事情比較好談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我出去一下囉,麥肯諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我已經克服怕狗的毛病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不用怕那個狗小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.66,0:09:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?三鷹先生要來的事\N妳還沒跟明日菜說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.46,0:09:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,因為我對這門親事\N一直沒什麼興致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為三鷹先生的女性關係嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為三鷹先生他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次來我們家都臉色發白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他身體不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我倒是沒聽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是別讓他跟明日菜見面好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.05,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.72,0:09:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從三鷹先生沒來看她以後\N明日菜就一直沒有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.93,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會不會是得了相思病?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是三鷹的叔叔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然來訪,請恕我冒昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.11,0:10:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?三鷹的叔叔來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你找我有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就單刀直入的說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳跟阿瞬分手好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳肯答應\N我一定會補償妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…談不上什麼分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你也太失禮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.42,0:11:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要給多少分手費?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-一之瀨太太!\N-一之瀨太太!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.09,0:11:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹和我不是那種特別關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.93,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他向妳求婚了,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,也僅止於此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不打算接受是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是阿瞬一廂情願啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.01,0:11:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.21,0:11:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託,不要隨便握她的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.28,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真抱歉\N這是我們家族的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.55,0:11:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下我就安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就圓滿解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員真是挑剔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.24,0:12:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連三鷹那麼好的對象\N她都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你的問題蠻多的\N但你還是好好加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,園長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史特洛賈諾夫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.72,0:13:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.64,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.85,0:14:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一件,不,這一件…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.23,0:14:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉,三鷹先生\N把你的西裝弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,請別放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.67,0:14:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼沒躲開呢?\N還抱住迎面而來的聖伯納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦,不自覺就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.61,0:14:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,明日菜\N妳可以下床了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.92,0:14:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼切入主題呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.73,0:15:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子她一直沒什麼精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.80,0:15:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,我已經好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這束花送給妳,祝妳康復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,好像沒有必要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒有必要哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.19,0:15:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我現在真的好感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.16,0:15:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她難道真的是得了相思病嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,臉色突然變好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看妳高興成這個樣子\N害我不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高興,好高興…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.08,0:15:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請三鷹先生來果然是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天還是先不要談好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.86,0:16:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠們是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的三鷹先生來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠們都很興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為明日菜生病不能陪牠們玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前牠們都無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來陪牠們運動一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不必麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.62,0:16:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續陪他們聊下去的話\N一定又會糾纏不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好乖,好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,要丟了,快去撿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.97,0:16:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生比以前有精神多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.60,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳自己愛瞎操心吧\N他本來就很健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.41,0:16:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,真的朝氣蓬勃\N而且很開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我自己進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.49,0:17:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的,我剛才去了\N傳聞中的寡婦那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寡婦沒有那個意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好乖,好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,能不能請你\N像以前一樣來打工呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為暑假的關係\N實習生都走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在人手不足,真的很頭痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.79,0:17:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我還沒找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會給你添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.60,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說\N你儘管去找工作沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.57,0:17:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不在的時候我會想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.84,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,待到找到新褓母為止就行了\N好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.95,0:18:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且孩子們都等著你來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,這樣真的好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.63,0:18:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的時期還去打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.54,0:18:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,而且我已經答應他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.57,0:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人真的很不懂得拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優柔寡斷的個性真的很吃虧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.81,0:18:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,或許可以轉換一下心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,就去轉換一下心情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你的下酒菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.46,0:18:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你怎麼了?\N表情好奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳做的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,看起來很好吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是看起來好吃而已喔\N你吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司…找到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹,我跟妳說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你到底打不打算去找公司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼打不打算,我已經無能為力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.83,0:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,五代老師怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代會怎麼樣都跟妳無關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼可以說爸爸是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋就是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.64,0:19:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,笨蛋,笨蛋…\N笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.52,0:19:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他突然變得好開朗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為能見到孩子們的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連公司倒閉的打擊都忘了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.66,0:19:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是五代的優點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是五代哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.01,0:20:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.85,0:20:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.02,0:20:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都過得好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.25,0:20:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好乖,好乖\N今天起又可以跟你們一起玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.22,0:20:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,來,好高好高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.86,0:20:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代肯回來\N真的幫了我們一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且孩子們真的好喜歡他喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.80,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧,好高好高…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳今天要用什麼手段\N說服妳爸爸呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼辦法都沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳什麼都不做嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.22,0:21:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.76,0:21:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們耳朵靠過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.81,0:21:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪小孩子玩真是累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.33,0:21:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八…八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.31,0:21:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次家父給你帶來很大的困擾\N真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.79,0:22:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又離家出走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.32,0:22:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在家父為你找到下一個工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.29,0:22:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且順利就職之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.63,0:22:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在五代老師身邊照顧你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.53,0:22:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.47,0:22:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還請各位,以及五代老師\N多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.21,0:22:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,妳太客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.41,0:22:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,老師\N晚飯已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.95,0:22:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,等一下,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.02,0:22:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位,失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.79,0:22:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,等一下,妳聽我說啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.36,0:22:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩真是學不會教訓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂年輕的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下該怎麼辦呢?管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.74,0:22:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能順其自然了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.41,0:22:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還蠻看得開的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.24,0:23:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.72,0:23:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦,對啊\N這是人家很努力做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.76,0:23:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,快點趁熱吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.33,0:23:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,老師,嘴巴張開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.73,0:23:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,八神妳在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.56,0:23:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係,又沒有人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.10,0:23:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒看到也聽得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,不要逃啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.27,0:23:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要鬧了!八神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.74,0:23:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,你的鼻子黏了飯粒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.55,0:23:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你拿下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.02,0:23:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要這樣啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.82,0:23:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要生氣囉!住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.46,0:23:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!三鷹拒絕了相親對象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.66,0:23:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還在眾目睽睽的墳前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要妳答應嫁給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.60,0:23:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下真的敲定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.90,0:23:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,不准他偷跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.24,0:23:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.77,0:24:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『我會等你的!\N響子突然的含意深深宣言』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.14,0:24:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.79,0:24:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.34,0:24:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.02,0:24:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.26,0:24:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.69,0:25:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.67,0:25:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.80,0:25:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.24,0:25:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.61,0:25:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
